How much does estate planning cost in Texas? A single number hides what work is included.

2
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:28,000
This is general education, not legal or financial advice. Fees vary by provider and scope.

3
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:54,000
A basic will is not the same scope as a coordinated plan. Compare the work included.

4
00:00:54,000 --> 00:01:19,000
The calculator's prefilled ranges are editable illustrations, not Texas averages or quotes.

5
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:47,000
Separate trust preparation from funding work. A signed trust does not automatically receive every asset.

6
00:01:47,000 --> 00:02:18,000
Texas has no universal probate percentage. Costs can follow different rules.

7
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:43,000
Preparation happens now. Administration may happen later. A comparison does not guarantee savings.

8
00:02:43,000 --> 00:03:05,000
